}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The S/N of the unit populating this entry is '''C40'''''1486678''. :The tag-line text on the hub's ''label'' (molded into the bottom casing) reads "Hi-Speed USB 2.0 7-Port Hub". "P81784" is also on the casing. :There is no revision / version info in the ''label''. It is ''presumed'' to be a rev. 1 unit..
The '''[[Belkin]]''' logo, "F5U237-C", and "REV:1.2/1.6mm" is silkscreened on the board. :The hub IC packages are labeled with "CY7C65640-LFC", "0423 D 04", "CYP 629507", and "KOR".
THe hub presents itself as two 050d:0237 devices to the host system.
